title: Fireside with the Underboss - "Joe Rogan Thinks I'm Good Looking"
description: Sammy's name is always being mentioned in the media in some way or another, but this time it's Joe Rogan who brings him into the conversation. Hear what Joe has to say about Sammy and Sammy reacts in real time to his comments.
